logs.message: TerraForgeServer depends on StackExchange.Redis (>= 2.7.0) but StackExchange.Redis 2.7.0 was not found. An approximate best match of StackExchange.Redis 2.7.4 was resolved.
Package 'MessagePack' 2.5.108 has a known moderate severity vulnerability, https://github.com/advisories/GHSA-4qm4-8hg2-g2xm
